<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 tīng wǒ xīn shēng dàn yuàn wǒ de guó jiā jìng wèi zhǔ, tīng wǒ xīn shēng dàn yuàn jūn wáng qǐ lái jìng bài zhǔ,
 tīng wǒ xīn shēng dàn yuàn wǒ de jiā rén fú shì zhǔ, tīng wǒ xīn shēng wǒ de nián rì shǔ yú zhǔ,
 qiú nǐ tīng wǒ qí qiú lián mǐn wǒ de guó jiā hé mín zú, guǎng xíng shè miǎn dà shī zhěng jiù,
 zhǔ qiú nǐ lián mǐn wǒ de guó jiā hé mín zú, yīn zhe yé sū de yuán gù.</lyrics>
<title>tīng wǒ xīn shēng 迦南146</title>
<hymn_number>146</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>